## commands

// Multiple cursors

hold ctrl

// Comments

ctrl + /

// Select next match, unselect next match

Ctrl + D
Ctrl + U

// Duplicate
Shift + Ctrl + D

// indent

ctrl + ]
ctrl + [

// move line up or down

ctrl + (up arrow)
ctrl + (down arrow)

## setup auto-indent keybind
// require atom restart

Edit > Keymap

'atom-text-editor':
    'ctrl-}': 'editor:auto-indent'

## auto-enable softwrap and Indent Guide

Edit > Config >

editor:
  showIndentGuide: true
  showInvisibles: true
  softWrap: true

## tools

apm install react

